      <title>印度尼西亚称海运不公平地偏袒自己的送货服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/sea-unfairly-favored-its-own-delivery-service-indonesia-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚反垄断机构正在调查东南亚电子商务领军企业 Sea Ltd.，因为该公司可能不公平地偏袒自己的送货服务而不是其他替代服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/sea-unfairly-favored-its-own-delivery-service-indonesia-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 06:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
